pullRequest.bodyText:
This adds a force-merge step to the searchable snapshot action, enabled by default,
but parameterizable using the `force_merge-index" optional boolean.
eg.
PUT _ilm/policy/my_policy
{
"policy": {
   "phases": {
     "cold": {
       "actions": {
         "searchable_snapshot" : {
           "snapshot_repository" : "backing_repo",
           "force_merge_index": true
         }
       }
     }
   }
 }
}

Relates to #53488
Closes #56215

commit.message:
ILM: add force-merge step to searchable snapshots action

This adds a force-merge step to the searchable snapshot action, enabled by default,
but parameterizable using the `force_merge-index" optional boolean.

eg.
```
PUT _ilm/policy/my_policy
{
  "policy": {
    "phases": {
      "cold": {
        "actions": {
          "searchable_snapshot" : {
            "snapshot_repository" : "backing_repo",
            "force_merge_index": true
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

